

Intent: It's a message passing mechanism between components of android except ContentProvider.
		You can use intent to start any component.

Sticky Intent : It sticks with android for future broad cast listeners. 
				Ex-if BATTERY_LOW event occurs then that intent will be stick with android so that 
				if in future battery low occurs while app is running that intent will be fired.

Pending Intent: If you want someone to perform any Intent operation at future point of time on behalf of you ,
				then we will use pending Intent. Ex- setting Alarm for some time .
				Example: http://www.sanfoundry.com/java-android-program-pending-intent/

				
